prompt:
Add relay_url and secret_file to the klaus webhook config in home/dev.nix.

## What to change

In `home/dev.nix`, the webhook block (lines 62-66) currently has port, path, and poll_fallback. Add two new fields:

```nix
webhook = {
  port = 9800;
  path = "/webhook/github";
  poll_fallback = false;
  relay_url = "https://classic-laddie.coin-inconnu.ts.net";
  secret_file = "/run/agenix/github-webhook-secret";
};
```

This enables the new `klaus webhook check` and `klaus webhook setup` commands (from klaus PR #170) to automatically configure GitHub repo webhooks.

## Constraints
- Only change the webhook block in home/dev.nix
- Do NOT touch any other files
- Do NOT run nixos-rebuild
